Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙海盗哥普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.22,0:01:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是真的好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.55,0:01:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过喝这么点就已经醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.22,0:01:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何在宇宙喝酒都会醉得很快的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.13,0:01:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样，帕夫金，还要来点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在操控飞船呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会喝酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是个可靠的司机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.42,0:01:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.47,0:01:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉，接下来我们要到哪里去？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找巴度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打倒沙拉曼达的话，就需要他的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:02:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在他在尼布特拉的极北地区
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怀念以前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕夫金，开快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到尼布特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.59,0:02:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置好像是2... 0... 9...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置209,X坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BC02
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.13,0:02:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们马上就要到达尼布特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除人工重力装置
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十九话 极北热血男
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪航班机303还有15分钟到达布鲁市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前我们正在穿越北极地区
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预定到达时间为20点15分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的心情如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说才好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近的景色只有一片雪景
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始就闷死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看到你那么美丽的大腿之后，心情就开始变好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人，那真是我的光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你马上可以看到美丽的巴斯亚大陆了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离目的地布鲁市还有四个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我没有记错的话，头等舱的话应该还有一个乘客的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.66,0:03:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙的话，他刚才就下机了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您还真喜欢开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.33,0:03:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人，请到这里来是为了工作的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是来观光旅行的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁市是个非常美丽的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想和像你这样的美女一起去观光一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但遗憾的是我的目的地不是布鲁市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这班机是通过北极直飞布鲁市的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,途中是什么地方都不停的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在中途下机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人在做些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在乘凉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来是想和你做朋友的，但是可惜我也要下机了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.93,0:03:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也差不多要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要到哪里去？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了，小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好风景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道格！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道格，你就不能再请点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是裸体在北极上空飞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然没有其它的民航班机来这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们用宇宙船在这里着陆不是更简单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了避开沙拉曼达的耳目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信他们不会在民用航班安排眼线的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们又不知道巴度那家伙在这里研究些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.35,0:05:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能他是在这里建个裸体主义的俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又或者是裸体衬衣之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想在火炉面前喝杯热咖啡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离巴度的研究所还有十公里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要到了那里的话，就能喝到热腾腾的白兰地和咖啡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴风雪就要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了那个声音的波长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:06:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那股气味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错那就是哥普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有道格和帕夫金也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们千万别来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个陷阱！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多应该能够看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像是看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道格，有没有看到巴度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有，任何人都没有看到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕夫金，停下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太不寻常了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙超人的听觉和狗一般的嗅觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该已经很清楚地知道我们已经来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经提前10天通知他了，不会不在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个太阳能系统没有向着太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就意味着太阳能系统没有启动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计算他不在家，也会打开太阳能系统的，这可是常识
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在北极如果能源用光的话那就死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说那个研究所已经很长时间没有人使用过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是巴度他发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现目标！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的坐标点为503，离研究所东北一公里的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇室队立即开始作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇室队B了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇室队C了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个好消息要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的老朋友看来是不远万里来这里看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不幸的是你见到将是他们三人的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.88,0:07:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我们呆在这里也不会有事发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我们先到巴度的研究所开作战会议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.08,0:08:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是陷阱！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找他们的尸体！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现一具疑似哥普拉的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这具尸体带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有战车返回本部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是队长，还有其他的两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要哥普拉死了，他们就是群乌合之众
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不配当我们的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脉搏为0
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑波停止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的机能都停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会用错的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳孔也开始放大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经彻底死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，巴度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你差不多可以加入我们了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭借个人的力量根本就没有办法忤逆我们基尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们打算以沙拉曼达为首领建立庞大的帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此我们需要像你这样的有前途的人才
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你一样拥有特殊能力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:10:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你的听觉视觉嗅觉比普通人灵敏一万倍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是光荣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因为这种能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才会十分讨厌你们身上的那股味道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好说话小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭借我们的技术实力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以替你进行脑科手术让你变成机械人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还不打算这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这么做的话有可能会破坏你的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带他出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐！我打算将皇室队全部调回前线基地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，贝拉莫大佐！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会负责将哥普拉的尸体运回本部的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了哥普拉的尸体，还要带上那个家伙一起回本部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天他的态度会转变得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇室队！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗得了他们可骗不到我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，巴度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好笑吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你发出的气味我就知道是道格你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还能记得我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太光荣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱险之后我倒想问问我的气味到底是怎么样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然我已经见到你了，但是我么应该怎么脱离这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们好像是在三号车的禁闭室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不用飞弹的话，我们根本就没有办法逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的事就交给哥普拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定有他的办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底要干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还在做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点杀了他！杀了他！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道格！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在三号车的上面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我要炸开车的侧面了.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，随时都可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉就在我们的上面！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想办法把他晃下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三号车的侧面被爆破了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉回头！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去干掉那个家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下全员到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么你不愿意助我们一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们仔细想清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.65,0:14:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭借我们四个就要和基尔顿作对的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是去送死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道忘了到底是谁救了你的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要我回报你们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂，要是你们不来的话，我也不会被他们给盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人各有志
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有必要去强迫别人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经厌倦了当海盗的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只想静静地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是要干到底！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是要我死！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的所有族人都是被他们给杀死的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接我的人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕鲸船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.79,0:15:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近岛上捕鱼为生的渔民
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们现在是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我就像是他们的家庭的一份子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好不容易在这里过上了普通人的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很重视着现在的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的生活！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是好东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人看起来挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:15:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都有点羡慕你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔顿也开始侵入这个地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会向西面去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到他们找不到我们为止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉为什么你要向基尔顿挑战！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至要拼上自己的性命呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了一个长发的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.61,0:16:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好保护好她！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.11,0:16:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航向西方！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无情的家伙，真的走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们放弃巴度那家伙，重新考虑计划吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙拉曼达的侦察机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.37,0:16:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它向西边飞去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇室队，这里是侦察机V2,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在坐标点770发现一艘捕鲸船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在向坐标点772移动中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是俘虏还是消灭他们？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来以为这一带的人已经全部被消灭了\N没想到竟然还有人活着！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们向西进发吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要抛弃你的朋友们呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经厌倦了那种生活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整日的杀来杀去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去我和他们都是海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海盗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我已经变了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的平和的生活改变了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我选择你而不是我的朋友!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这么做真的好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静点？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.21,0:17:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:17:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是基尔顿的战车！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它朝我们来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右满舵！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快调头！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！风太大了不能转舵！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:18:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴度！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:18:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露莎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露莎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露莎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟她一起去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.12,0:19:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊，你还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你的运气确实很强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再让你跑掉的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要亲手要了你的性命！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道认为就凭你的精神感应枪就能打败我的战车吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这辆皇室战车可是用300毫米的重合金制成的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.69,0:20:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何大炮都不能破坏它！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉，你快逃吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭你的精神感应枪是对付不了他的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎是太小看我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.41,0:20:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材！临死前做无谓的挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.61,0:20:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你下地狱去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神感应枪的热力模糊了我的视野
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能一直维持下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:21:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你的精神力量用尽之时就是你的死期了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.81,0:21:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.82,0:21:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.92,0:21:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.09,0:21:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错这战车的装甲能够扛得住精神感应枪发出的高热
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.43,0:21:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是坐在里面的人可受不了这么高的温度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉你要达到沙拉曼达的理由到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么就算是要拼上性命也要对付他们？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.22,0:22:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么理由只是强烈的感情因素
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.09,0:22:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇的血在我的身体里沸腾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要为我心爱的人报仇！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.03,0:22:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要亲手干掉那个家伙\N就算是要我下地狱也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.87,0:22:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这一点也不像你，但是现在的我能了解你的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴还等着我们！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
